---
title: Irish Sirloin Steak and Sofrito Potatoes with Cajun spices and pan-fried broccoli
description: Butter-basted cajun sirloin steak, peppery potatoes, and tender pan-fried broccoli combine for a meal that's beautifully balanced and melt-in-mouth delicious.
